{"id": 2715, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都因为操心啥睡不着过？", "description": "也没啥事，不过就是睡前立了个“今天一定早睡早起”的 flag……（题图来自：iStock ©️ id-work）", "record_count": 2515, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190103144938K4IoiU7plgfaMj3u.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-09T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 321792, "content": "怕明天的到来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367444}, {"id": 321793, "content": "做兼职呀呀呀呀呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416200}, {"id": 322561, "content": "操心中国教育这么落后，大学还有8人间，没热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557189}, {"id": 321794, "content": "考试周日常操心成绩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132460}, {"id": 321795, "content": "没人睡我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 321796, "content": "高考", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009176}, {"id": 322052, "content": "明天一大早回老家的火车，怕起不来。🙃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1263479}, {"id": 321797, "content": "碌碌无为", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553381}, {"id": 321798, "content": "要期末考呀，焦虑不安。\n还有要出门玩兴奋的。\n专业知识考核，内容太多了通宵背看呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553371}, {"id": 322054, "content": "假如中了一个亿怎么用 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497726}, {"id": 321799, "content": "饿！", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397575}, {"id": 321800, "content": "为操心睡不着觉而睡不着觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391907}, {"id": 326664, "content": "学生会的事情没做完/明天有哪些事情要做", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578458}, {"id": 321801, "content": "在想，我特么是个傻子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552213}, {"id": 322057, "content": "男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554423}, {"id": 324617, "content": "会因为某件事引起焦虑时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567272}, {"id": 321802, "content": "球赛，考试，陪自己熬夜的男生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 321803, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178586}, {"id": 321804, "content": "我好想没有呢我是个沾床就睡，对了其实我倒是有个好办法入眠，上床，啥也不想，闭着眼就困了呢，困不着，在床上坐着，读一本你看不懂的专业书籍，十几分钟后入睡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553394}, {"id": 322060, "content": "午夜时分，欲望膨胀。想要太多，则为之束缚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554381}, {"id": 330509, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599241}, {"id": 321805, "content": "催婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542376}, {"id": 321806, "content": "脑补自己扣篮，越想越兴奋", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534218}, {"id": 322062, "content": "假期即将结束 究极焦虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186868}, {"id": 321807, "content": "操心睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115890}, {"id": 322319, "content": "太用心了，睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348207}, {"id": 321808, "content": "女生表达的是什么，到底在想什么(‖´_ゝ｀)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250893}, {"id": 322576, "content": "高考😅", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929748}, {"id": 321809, "content": "面临毕业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553409}, {"id": 321810, "content": "焦虑！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553411}, {"id": 322066, "content": "怎么处理异地恋，没有业绩怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544583}, {"id": 321811, "content": "就是单纯的恐惧，担忧，无来由的恐慌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128485}, {"id": 322067, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554456}, {"id": 321812, "content": "自己在家死了没人发现怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869835}, {"id": 322836, "content": "刚和男（女）朋友在一起时，那种兴奋感会让人翻来覆去睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556911}, {"id": 320533, "content": "明天赶早飞机，万一起不来咋整", "image": null, "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321813, "content": "都是考试，高考，驾考，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534831}, {"id": 322581, "content": "回家过周末，星期五晚上累到早早睡，星期六晚上精神的听着楼下同楼邻居喝茶闲聊，星期天回到宿舍又是玩手机补剧晚睡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310603}, {"id": 320534, "content": "金庸老爷子过世了，我担心小龙女张无忌他们太难过，得去看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321814, "content": "我学不完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455119}, {"id": 321815, "content": "考数学", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538937}, {"id": 321816, "content": "兄弟在外打拼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553421}, {"id": 321817, "content": "以后没钱花🌸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553427}, {"id": 321818, "content": "我男朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552145}, {"id": 321819, "content": "穷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 321820, "content": "人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551772}, {"id": 321821, "content": "明天结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 320542, "content": "我不忍心让手机一个人孤零零躺在桌子上，想多陪它一会", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321822, "content": "明天放假", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553447}, {"id": 321823, "content": "她这会都还不想睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577726}]}